{"tid":888334,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"慶幸活喺呢個年代 見證住另一隊香港殿堂樂隊嘅誕生","createTime":"2018-11-03T16:00:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-05T04:16:42.000Z","uid":151058,"like":8,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"adbb482c4f1374439b18742aa19fb7a2a4716664","tid":888334,"uid":151058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T16:00:17.000Z","msg":"十二年第一場紅館 <br />\n我地聽到嘅唔止係好聽多變嘅旋律 唔止係超曬班嘅技巧<br />\n我地聽到嘅係靈魂 係內心<br />\n好開心前排有個post講eason嘅時候 大家開始除去左以往嘅&lsquo;上一輩光環&rsquo; <br />\n期待呢一隊樂隊一步一步向前走 帶住佢地音樂上嘅多變 人生上嘅堅持 有一日實至名歸咁坐上寶座<br />\n佢地係我地呢一代香港人嘅 Supper Moment"},{"pid":"8c39ddf61bca618ae92794dccc94e6bdf26fc3e1","tid":888334,"uid":190187,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T16:02:33.000Z","msg":"唔係話佢地廢，但係講到殿堂級又誇得滯喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a83d835b2e9b403b1775cb65ef00c6a20fb79b","tid":888334,"uid":151058,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T16:04:24.000Z","msg":"可能佢地未到嗰種唱到街知巷聞嘅程度<br />\n但我希望有一日 一講起佢地連二千年以後嘅小朋友都會唱得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"110f2bef19f584caf3b3d345e2cc1ae29f39ca5b","tid":888334,"uid":186882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T04:13:58.000Z","msg":"呢一代計19 算係新beyond啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62c68a38db3399baa361dafad1370cb47f760d35","tid":888334,"uid":5218,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T04:16:42.000Z","msg":"殿堂？！邊忽殿邊忽堂？"}]}